.DT
is_allowed_to_modify_account
$MUDNAME$ Creator Help
is_allowed_to_modify_account

.SH Name
.SP 5 5
is_allowed_to_modify_account -  This method checks to see if the specified person is allowed to access the account.
.EP

.SH Syntax
.SI 5
int is_allowed_to_modify_account(string club_name,
string account,
string person)
.EI

.SH Parameters
.SI 5
%^BOLD%^club_name%^RESET%^ - the name of the club
%^BOLD%^account%^RESET%^ - the name of the account
%^BOLD%^person%^RESET%^ - the person's name to check
.EI

.SH Returns
.SI 5
1 if they can access the account, 0 if they cannot
.EI

.SH Defined in
.SI 5
/handlers/inherit/club_elected.c
.EI

.SH Description
.SP 5 5

This method checks to see if the specified person is allowed to
access the account.  It checks based on both position and name.
.EP

.SH See also
.SP 5 5
query_account_allowed_people(), add_money(), remove_money(), query_account_allowed_positions()

.EP

